{"tid":1121644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]其實點解印度人會咁臭","createTime":"2019-04-23T12:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T12:58:27.000Z","uid":250027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b824c7594fc41405d5fee787d24edd36de8e141","tid":1121644,"uid":250027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:37:26.000Z","msg":"間唔中翻工放工撘車都會有印度人同一卡<br />\n非種族歧視<br />\n但真心係有一陣異味<br />\n以前有印度同學會噴好多古龍水去掩飾下<br />\n但都仲係會聞到果陣味<br />\n而且我發現每個印度人陣味都好似<br />\n到底呢陣味係點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f68fce71e9adc629bd58401135430f6138b778","tid":1121644,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab72d1798b98204bb3cd5b207375da179932fc1a","tid":1121644,"uid":250027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50f68fce71e9adc629bd58401135430f6138b778","tid":1121644,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"好奇想知白人係咪又會覺得黃種人有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有印度同學係英國土生土長都係會有果陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2b82f505b5ec6883f8483fc3e5bb57804b41bd","tid":1121644,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"佢地為左慳錢就算一身汗唔沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca65df255b122bb0d129afba1c3b2a0e78a5b01","tid":1121644,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11ea66ce674d37590f12e6912d274b84ca262998","tid":1121644,"uid":225364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"飲食習慣"},{"pid":"e534bd6e7